 11 │ The Grafana dashboard highlighted the key metric: `process.memoryUsage()`. The ‘used’ column was steadily increasing, particularly the ‘heapUsed’ value. This immediately suggested a memory leak – something was accumulating within the process without being released. We set up an alert to trigger when `heapUsed` exceeded 75% of the worker's total memory, hoping to catch it early.
    ·                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  ─────────────┬────────────
