 45 │ 
 46 │ Ultimately, tracking down this memory leak was a testament to the power of systematic investigation, combined with a deep understanding of our application’s architecture and potential pitfalls. It served as a stark reminder that even seemingly well-designed code can harbor unexpected ghosts if not carefully monitored and managed.  And it's a story we now use internally to emphasize the importance of robust event listener management – a lesson that saved us significant time, resources, and potentially, a major production outage.
    · ─────┬────
